OL,4,CApology for forced adoption 'would
OL,5,Cheal' Scottish women's shame
OL,6, A Scottish mother forced to give her
OL,7, baby up for adoption in the 1970s says
OL,8, an apology for the cruel practice would
OL,9, "lift women out of shame".
OL,11,FThe Scottish government is facing calls
OL,12,Fto issue an official apology to
OL,13,FScottish mothers who were pressured
OL,14,Finto giving up their children.
OL,16,FIt is estimated 60,000 women had babies
OL,17,Fadopted simply because they were
OL,18,Funmarried.
OL,20,FMSPs debated the issue of a government
OL,21,Fapology at Holyrood on Wednesday.
